&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;5bhoaz&quot; data-start=&quot;2059&quot; data-end=&quot;2179&quot;&gt;Proven experience leading compliance audits, certification programs, and multi-jurisdictional regulatory requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;xc8qc8&quot; data-s

&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about people, culture, and building great workplaces? Do you want hands-on experience in a dynamic, international company operating at the forefront of environmental markets? Then this internship at ACT Group might be the perfect opportunity for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an HR Intern, you will become part of our HR team, supporting a fast-growing international organization. You will gain valuable experience across multiple HR topics while working closely with experienced HR professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Role in Our Story:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In essence, your role involves:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
