&lt;li&gt;Helping maintain and update HR systems and employee records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting HR projects related to employee engagement, learning &amp;amp; development, or employee branding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting with internal communication and HR initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
