&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This internship offers a unique opportunity to gain hands-on, real world HR experience in a fast-paced international trading environment. You will work closely with experienced HR professionals and gain exposure to various HR projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for candidates with the following qualifications and attributes:&lt;/p&gt;
